com.exedio.cope.instrument

Annotation Type WrapperType


  • @Target(value=TYPE)
 @Retention(value=SOURCE)
public @interface WrapperType

    • Element Detail

      • type

        public abstract Visibility type
        Overrides the visibility of the generated TYPE constant. The visibility defaults to the visibility of the class.
        Default:
        com.exedio.cope.instrument.Visibility.DEFAULT

      • constructor

        public abstract Visibility constructor
        Overrides the visibility of the generated initial constructor.

        The initial constructor takes arguments for each initial feature. Features are initial if they do implement Settable and Settable.isInitial() returns true. This can be overridden by WrapperInitial.

        The visibility defaults to the "most private" visibility of all initial features set by the constructor. However, the constructor is not "more public" than the class.

        Default:
        com.exedio.cope.instrument.Visibility.DEFAULT

      • genericConstructor

        public abstract Visibility genericConstructor
        Overrides the visibility of the generated generic constructor, that calls Item.Item(com.exedio.cope.SetValue...). The visibility defaults to "private" for final classes, and "protected" for non-final classes.
        Default:
        com.exedio.cope.instrument.Visibility.DEFAULT

      • activationConstructor

        public abstract Visibility activationConstructor
        Overrides the visibility of the generated activation constructor, that calls Item.Item(com.exedio.cope.ActivationParameters). The visibility defaults to "private" for final classes, and "protected" for non-final classes.
        Default:
        com.exedio.cope.instrument.Visibility.DEFAULT

      • indent

        public abstract int indent
        Default:
        1

      • comments

        public abstract boolean comments
        Default:
        true
